@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

cloud "Partner Network" as Partner
rectangle "Extranet Zone\nPartner Gateway" as PGW
rectangle "Integration Services\nValidate + Transform" as IntSvc
rectangle "Internal API Gateway" as IAGW
queue "Message Bus" as MQ
rectangle "Core Services" as Core

Partner --> PGW : B2B API/SFTP/MQ
PGW --> IntSvc : Contract + auth policy
IntSvc --> IAGW : Normalized payload
IAGW --> Core : Internal API call
IAGW --> MQ : Async events
MQ --> Core : Consumption
Core --> IAGW : Response/event ack
IAGW --> IntSvc
IntSvc --> PGW
PGW --> Partner

note right of PGW
Per-partner isolation,
credentials, and throttling.
end note
@enduml

